description: I believe that for Music Lovers organiing songs into folders is a big problem, so here comes a simple solution to that problem. Just run the Mp3fm app and follow the instructions to Pack the Songs into folders corresponding to the properties chosen by you from Album(Movie)YearArtistTitle.
